high_descs: Turn to the left, walk until you reach the door, then turn to the left to face the kitchen counter.
Pick up the potato that is on the counter.
Walk around the counter until you are facing the stove.
Place the potato in the microwave that is above the stove, cooking it before pulling it back out.
Turn to your right and walk up to the refrigerator.
Put the potato inside of the fridge, in front of the white plate, and close the door.
